WEBVTT

00:04.019 --> 00:05.480
<i>I'll be gone in a week.</i>

00:05.480 --> 00:06.730
Your mother'll miss you.

00:06.730 --> 00:08.650
- Taking her with me, Alan.
- What?

00:08.650 --> 00:10.190
<i>She barely knows
what year it is.</i>

00:10.190 --> 00:12.070
Take off your shoes.
You know your father

00:12.070 --> 00:14.030
won't abide
any click-clacks in the house.

00:14.030 --> 00:15.620
<i>They call it sundownin'.</i>

00:15.620 --> 00:17.450
<i>Nights are hard for your mom.</i>

00:23.540 --> 00:24.870
<i>Warden Lacy,</i>

00:24.870 --> 00:28.250
he told me the Devil was a boy,

00:28.250 --> 00:30.460
and old Dale said he caught him.

00:30.460 --> 00:33.170
<i>Had locked the Devil in a box.</i>

00:33.170 --> 00:36.140
<i>To put an end to all
the horrors we've seen,</i>

00:36.140 --> 00:38.050
<i>that's what God told me.</i>

00:38.050 --> 00:39.680
How long ago was this?

00:39.680 --> 00:41.470
<i>Don't let
that fuckin' kid out.</i>

00:41.470 --> 00:43.230
Is it time to call Pruitt?

00:43.230 --> 00:46.310
Hey! I can be your lawyer
if you want me to be.

00:46.310 --> 00:48.520
- But you have to say it.
<i>- We're both</i>

00:48.520 --> 00:49.610
gettin' out of this shithole.

